h2 Course Participation
- views = {}
- data.each { |activity| views[activity['date']] = activity['views'] }
h3 Views
== line_chart views
| #{views}
h3 Participations
- participations = {}
- data.each { |activity| participations[activity['date']] = activity['participations'] }
== line_chart participations
/ == line_chart Hash[participations.group_by_day { |u| u[0] }.map { |k, v| v.size == 0 ? [k, v.size] : [k, v[0][1]] }]
| #{participations}
